---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Technical Standards & Guides | LRA Cloud Operations"
  descripcion="Engineering standards we apply on every engagement. Terraform module patterns, GitOps workflows and Kubernetes production guidelines based on real deployments."
  keywords="DevOps engineering standards, Terraform best practices guide, GitOps standards, Kubernetes production guide"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 110%, rgba(30,111,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 65%);"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-24 text-center"
    >
      <div
        class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6 text-xs"
        style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);"
      >
        <a
          href="/"
          style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);"
          class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a
        >
        <span>/</span>
        <span style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.9);">Docs</span>
      </div>
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        Technical Documentation
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Technical Standards & Guides
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);"
      >
        Engineering standards we apply on every engagement. Based on real
        production deployments in healthcare, fintech and SaaS environments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DOCS GRID -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">
        <!-- Terraform Standards -->
        <a
          href="/docs/terraform-standards"
          class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200"
          style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top: 4px solid #7B42BC; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08); text-decoration: none;"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5 flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7B42BC 0%, #5B2E9E 100%);"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span
            class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block"
            style="color: #7B42BC;">Terraform</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-base font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-[#7B42BC] transition-colors"
            style="color: #0A2540;"
          >
            Terraform Standards
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1" style="color: #64748b;">
            Module structure, remote state, variable naming, OIDC authentication
            and environment separation patterns.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #7B42BC;"
            >Read guide →</span
          >
        </a>

        <!-- GitOps Standards -->
        <a
          href="/docs/gitops-standards"
          class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200"
          style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top: 4px solid #FF6C37; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08); text-decoration: none;"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5 flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6C37 0%, #C04A1E 100%);"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span
            class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block"
            style="color: #FF6C37;">GitOps</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-base font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-[#FF6C37] transition-colors"
            style="color: #0A2540;"
          >
            GitOps Standards
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1" style="color: #64748b;">
            Repository structure, ArgoCD setup, Helm values per environment,
            sync policies and secret management with OIDC.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #FF6C37;"
            >Read guide →</span
          >
        </a>

        <!-- Kubernetes Production -->
        <a
          href="/docs/kubernetes-production"
          class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200"
          style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top: 4px solid #326CE5; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08); text-decoration: none;"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5 flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #326CE5 0%, #1A4DB5 100%);"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span
            class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block"
            style="color: #326CE5;">Kubernetes</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-base font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-[#326CE5] transition-colors"
            style="color: #0A2540;"
          >
            Kubernetes Production Guide
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1" style="color: #64748b;">
            Resource requests/limits, health checks, pod security standards,
            network policies and HPA configuration.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #326CE5;"
            >Read guide →</span
          >
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Note -->
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4"
        style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"
      >
        <div
          class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
          style="background: #EEF4FF;"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            style="color: #1E6FFF;"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
            Based on real production work
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
            These are the actual standards our team applies on every engagement
            — not theoretical guidelines. They reflect decisions we have made
            and validated in production across healthcare, financial services
            and SaaS environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Need help applying these standards?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-sm mb-7 max-w-xl mx-auto"
        style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);"
      >
        We can implement these patterns in your environment. Schedule a free
        technical review.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-7 py-3.5 rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]"
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E6FFF 0%, #1452cc 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);"
      >
        Schedule free consultation
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          ><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
